# 📦 Product Management API Documentation

## Base URL
```
http://localhost:5000/api/products
```

---

## 🔐 Authentication

Most vendor routes require authentication. Include the JWT token in the header:

```
Authorization: Bearer <your_jwt_token>
```

---

## 📚 API Endpoints Overview

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|--------|----------|--------|-------------|
| POST | `/` | Vendor | Add new product |
| PUT | `/:productId` | Vendor | Update product |
| DELETE | `/:productId` | Vendor | Delete product |
| GET | `/:productId` | Public | Get single product |
| GET | `/` | Public | Get all products |
| GET | `/vendor/my-products` | Vendor | Get vendor's products |
| GET | `/category/:categoryId` | Public | Get products by category |
| GET | `/search/all` | Public | Search products |
| GET | `/featured/all` | Public | Get featured products |
| GET | `/related/:productId` | Public | Get related products |
| PATCH | `/:productId/status` | Vendor | Update product status |
| PATCH | `/:productId/stock` | Vendor | Update product stock |
| GET | `/check-delivery/:productId` | Public | Check delivery availability |

