**Variant IDs Explanation:**
- `"1 3"` = Size: Small (id=1) + Color: Blue (id=3)
- `"1 4"` = Size: Small (id=1) + Color: Red (id=4)
- `"2 3"` = Size: Medium (id=2) + Color: Blue (id=3)
- `"2 4"` = Size: Medium (id=2) + Color: Red (id=4)

