## 💡 Tips & Best Practices

1. **Always set main image** - Required for product listing
2. **Use special prices** - Increases conversions
3. **Add detailed descriptions** - Improves SEO
4. **Set proper stock levels** - Prevents overselling
5. **Enable COD wisely** - Based on your logistics
6. **Use tags effectively** - Improves searchability
7. **Set cancelable_till properly** - Based on your fulfillment speed
8. **For variable products** - Ensure all variants have stock data
9. **Digital products** - Always provide download link or file
10. **Test delivery** - Use check-delivery endpoint before showing to customers

