## 🔄 Workflow Example

### Complete Product Lifecycle:

```
1. Vendor adds product → Status: Pending
2. Admin approves → isApproved: true
3. Vendor activates → isActive: true
4. Product visible to customers → Gets orders
5. Stock decreases → Auto update
6. Low stock alert → Vendor restocks
7. Out of stock → stockStatus: 0
8. Vendor restocks → stockStatus: 1
9. End of season → Vendor deactivates → isActive: false
10. Next season → Vendor reactivates
```

